員被中共特務傷殘之後，武警大開殺戒，鎮壓香港，挽回面子。今日，中港大決戰的前夕，美國參議員盧比奧向中國發出最強烈的警告。<br />\n各位香港人，如果可以忍住，請撤離今明兩日泛民舉辦的示威，避免共匪製造事端，不要辜負美方的一片好心。泛民在今明兩日忽然故此勇武衝鋒，大家如果不是傻的，應該知道原因的吧。<br />\n當然，如果你要充當共匪的打手，要做中共屠殺香港民權運動的引路人，那隨便你。"},{"pid":"1322ac0cb17965e0dea9caa27c6882ad43754924","tid":1479871,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nP牌無罪，國師有理<br />\n大家一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e6f20b7434f29fb59270d704d80c05eafa67c1","tid":1479871,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:13:14.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n<br />\nP牌無罪，國師有理<br />\n大家一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fe5580b0be8f9f8e30e8efe637839fd57ed474","tid":1479871,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:13:35.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\nP牌無罪，國師有理<br />\n大家一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66dfd3a5308a26926fba94e9f91ea42a40873893","tid":1479871,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\nP牌無罪，國師有理<br />\n大家一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492c699519edf42baeb691daeff8d67646dfc375","tid":1479871,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:14:26.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\nP牌無罪，國師有理<br />\n大家一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119ca827006067283ef6c1eb0b62c51adf7306a0","tid":1479871,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:16:29.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\nP牌無罪，國師有理<br />\n大家一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae1e3702ad500d1daf080f272f25d08050935f6","tid":1479871,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:16:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\nP牌無罪，國師有理<br />\n大家一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a275e7b18c7931927387507ab920df71396fe6","tid":1479871,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:16:54.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\nP牌無罪，國師有理<br />\n大家一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5128ba5d69fd30d0a0f5bd798043d75b5b94a982","tid":1479871,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"From 超級「和理非」：<br />\n<br />\n明天情況有點複雜，不像以往的遊行。<br />\n不得不防警察、公安、黑社會的共同部署。作為超級和理非，我認為必需注意安全。我們不能退讓，也不能錯誤犯險。簡單來說，明天安全大於一切。<br />\n我讚成排隊進入維園，但不同意「迫爆」任何地方，包括維園。「迫爆」一個地方是很危險的，資訊變得封閉，容易造謠傳謠，容易讓邪惡勢力有機可乘。機場集會就是這個情況。因此，保持流動性十分重要。<br />\n比較可取的做法，是在各區排隊進入維園，按情況隨時離隊入隊，隨時可以去到安全的地方，不阻塞，不犯險。我認為是對自己和對其他人最負責任的做法。"},{"pid":"7d1c433bc17598c7029a9379247947fe9dc34770","tid":1479871,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:42:38.000Z","msg":"推"}]}